IndexAnalyzerAttribute IndexAnalyzerAttribute Class

In this Article

Edit

Indicates that the Field generated by FieldBuilder for the target property should have its IndexAnalyzer property set to the specified analyzer.

Syntax

Declaration

[AttributeUsage(AttributeTargets.Property)]
public class IndexAnalyzerAttribute : Attribute, _Attribute<AttributeUsage(AttributeTargets.Property)>
